name: Commander Gherant
Lore: 'Deck officer aboard the Super Star Destroyer Executor. Responsible for preventing unauthorized access to sensitive areas of the Empire''s flagship. Hand-picked by Captain Piett.',
Text: 'If aboard Executor (even at an Executor site), once during each of your deploy phases, may use 2 Force to search your Reserve Deck and take any one Executor site into hand. Shuffle, cut and replace.',
